12 to subsection (a) to read as follows:
13 "(8) No contract shall be awarded or entered into by the Department of Administrative
14 Services or any state agency if such contract was solicited pursuant to a request for
15 proposals that includes consideration of transgender issues as any part of a factor or
16 criterion in the evaluation."
